<p>Hi <%= @resource.email %>,</p>

<p>Someone requested a password reset for your <strong>HeyBob</strong> account. Click the link below to set a new password:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Reset My Password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>This link will expire in <%= Devise.reset_password_within / 3600 %> hours.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email — your password won't change.</p>

<p>— The HeyBob Team</p>
